        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/migrating-to-2.0.dita" xtrc="p:1;25:12">XSLT stylesheets were converted to XSLT 2.0. With that change, variable types were also
          implemented. Plug-ins that change template variable values will need to make the following
          changes:</p>
        <ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/migrating-to-2.0.dita" xtrc="ul:1;28:13">
