      <section class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/migrating-to-2.0.dita" xtrc="section:3;38:16">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/migrating-to-2.0.dita" xtrc="title:3;39:16">All transformations — refactoring</title>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/migrating-to-2.0.dita" xtrc="p:3;40:12">Much of the toolkit code was refactored for release 2.0. Customization changes that were
          based on a specific template in a previous version of the toolkit might not work because
          the modified template is no longer used. If this is the case, the changes will need to be
          reimplemented based on the new XSLT templates.</p>
